---
import Cta from '../components/home/Cta-Contact.astro';
import Options from '../components/brand-strategy/Options.astro';
import Hero from '../components/home/Slot-HeroFullscreen.astro';
import IntroSec from '../components/brand-strategy/Intro-Webdesign-Sec.astro';
import OptionsSec from '../components/brand-strategy/Options-Secondary.astro';
import Grid from '../components/brand-strategy/Grid-Webdesign.astro';
import GridSec from '../components/brand-strategy/Grid-Webdesign-Sec.astro';
import IndentInfo from '../components/home/Slot-Indent-Info.astro';
import Faq from '../components/brand-strategy/Faq.astro';
import SectionHeadImg from "../components/home/slot-img.astro";
import SectionHeadSecImg from "../components/home/slot-img-rev.astro";
import Process from '../components/home/Process.astro';
import FirstProcess from '../components/home/Process-Sml.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

let backgroundUrl = 'url(/works/billboard-design.webp)' // Define image for Slot-HeroFullscreen and then call BackgroundURL in Section
---

<Layout
  description="Brand stategy development for the age of e-commerce. Graphic design for print and digital. 3D design for video and product development."
  title="Brand Strategy and Graphic Design Â· Aidxn Web Design"
>
  
<Hero backgroundUrl={backgroundUrl}>
  <Fragment slot="smltitle">
    Brand Strategy & Graphic Design
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="title">
    Improve Sales Through Design
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="desc">
    With the right brand strategy, I'll help you establish a brand identity that communicates to your customer.
  </Fragment>
</Hero>

<FirstProcess />

<Options />

<OptionsSec />

<SectionHeadImg>
  <Fragment slot="smltitle">
    Beyond digital design: from Shopfronts to Websites to Billboards
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="title">
    Not just another digital marketing agency.
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="desc">
    Graphic design is the visual language that your brand speaks. Every image, color, and font choice conveys a message. With my graphic design expertise, I'll transform your ideas into visually appealing and impactful designs. From logos to marketing materials, I ensure that your brand's visual identity is consistent and unforgettable. In an era of digital marketing, sometimes going beyond the screen can make a remarkable impact. By tapping into traditional advertising mediums like billboards and buses, your brand can reach a broader audience. I'm here to help you bridge the gap between old-school and new-school marketing, ensuring that no potential customer is left undiscovered. Your brand's physical presence is as crucial as its online identity. I offer a holistic redesign approach, refreshing your shopfront's appearance and interiors. A revamped, modern shopfront paired with an updated online platform powered by the latest Velocity web design ensures that your brand makes a memorable impression from the street to the web.
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="cover">
    <img
              src="/works/ax-sqr-cpc-results.webp"
              class="w-full"
            />
  </Fragment>
</SectionHeadImg>

<SectionHeadSecImg>
  <Fragment slot="smltitle">
    Lasting branding guidelines that are easy to stick to.
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="title">
    Consistently designed brand guidelines.
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="desc">
    Consistency is the backbone of effective branding. I help create brand guidelines that serve as a roadmap for using your visual elements. From color codes to logo usage, these guidelines ensure that your brand maintains its identity across various mediums. The branding process doesn't stop at the initial design. I work with you to create brand strategies that can withstand the test of time. Whether you're launching a startup or revitalizing an established business, I ensure that your brand can adapt and thrive in an ever-evolving marketplace. Ready to embark on a journey of branding and graphic design excellence? Contact me, and let's elevate your brand to new heights.    
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="cover">
    <img
              src="/works/ax-sqr-re-placement.webp"
              class="w-full"
            />
  </Fragment>
</SectionHeadSecImg>

<IntroSec />

<Grid />

<IndentInfo>
  <Fragment slot="title">
    Logo design
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="desc"> 
    Your logo is often the first thing people see when they encounter your brand. It should be distinctive and memorable. I have a knack for creating compelling logos that capture the essence of your business. I ensure that your logo stands out in a crowded marketplace and leaves a lasting impression.
  </Fragment>
</IndentInfo>

<Faq />

<IndentInfo>
  <Fragment slot="title">
    Colour palettes and fonts
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="desc"> 
    The colors and fonts you choose play a pivotal role in shaping your brand's personality. I understand the psychology behind colors and typography, ensuring that your brand elements resonate with your target audience. Whether it's a playful and vibrant palette or a sleek and modern font, I'll guide you to the right choices.
  </Fragment>
</IndentInfo>

<GridSec />

<Cta />

<Process />
  
</Layout>
